room_title: Escape room "Skull and Scepter" by Break Through Sac in Sacramento
room_address: 1338 Howe Ave, Building B Suite 200, Sacramento, CA 95825
room_description: Famous artifacts and artworks are being stolen from all over the world. Your investigations have led you to the radical religious sect known as The Order of the Skull and Scepter. Unravel a labyrinth of mysteries and secrets as you infiltrate the Order's bunker and put a stop to their crime spree. But beware... the Order will stop at nothing to make sure their plans are fulfilled.
